criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Major patient;

          -  Indication of curative intent radiotherapy for breast cancer treated with conservative
             treatment. Accepted radiotherapy scheme: 50 Gy (main) + 16 Gy on the tumor bed
             (additional dose);

          -  Patient affiliated or entitled to a social security scheme;

          -  Patient who signed an informed consent form.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnant or lactating woman;

          -  Legal incapacity or limited legal capacity. Medical or psychological conditions that
             do not allow the subject to understand the study and sign the consent

          -  Patient followed by a liberal homeopath;

          -  Patient with bilateral breast cancer;

          -  Patient with in situ breast cancer;

          -  Patient with known cognitive impairment;

          -  Patient with known allergy and / or intolerance and / or malabsorption to fructose,
             glucose, galactose;

          -  Patient with a known deficiency in sucrase / isomaltase / lactase.
